reviewText: Excellent coming of age type movie where most of the passion is implied and felt by the viewer, but not explicitly seen. Filmed primarily along the European beach, a young man must reckon with the ecstasy and calamity of having 3 relationships at the same time. His ultimate solution comes as a complete surprise and leaves you wishing for a sequel.
Classic French cultural film.  Was good, but not quite up to the reviews I read.
